    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/3a0d39aee4f279a981c390524786a4ac.poster.avif?t=1771774128\" width=780 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/3a0d39aee4f279a981c390524786a4ac.webm?t=1771774128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/3a0d39aee4f279a981c390524786a4ac.mp4?t=1771774128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Axom: Conquest 是一款坚守型塔防 Roguelite 游戏，专为喜爱用超强流派“打破游戏”的策略玩家打造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造一座坚不可摧的堡垒，解锁保龄球塔、核弹，以及一个名叫 Jeff 的小机器人。抵御成千上万由物理驱动的无情外星虫群，并解锁强大的元进程系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/636a33c9badabb275135018e8fc921ff.webp?t=1771774128\" width=616 height=4 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造你的堡垒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/35499a5e37a2e53568475c8622226a0c.poster.avif?t=1771774128\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/35499a5e37a2e53568475c8622226a0c.webm?t=1771774128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/35499a5e37a2e53568475c8622226a0c.mp4?t=1771774128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造一座庞大的堡垒 - 保护你的 Nexus Drill，抵御无尽的 Centurax 虫群。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩展你的经济 - 向外扩张，通过炼油厂等设施开采 Axom 的资源！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每一局都独一无二</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/0845bd94ce2820bddfbe632ce90aff0f.poster.avif?t=1771774128\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/0845bd94ce2820bddfbe632ce90aff0f.webm?t=1771774128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/0845bd94ce2820bddfbe632ce90aff0f.mp4?t=1771774128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局都真正独特 – 互相联动的系统、程序生成地图、分支塔防路线、升级链、外星升级、独特敌人以及改变战局的消耗品，让每次游玩都截然不同。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十种起始职业 – 每局开始前选择一种 Nexus 变体，每种都有独特属性与能力，引导你的策略走向偏好的玩法风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >外星感染 - 在星球本身排斥你存在的同时平衡进攻与防守。被感染的地块会逐渐扩散，迫使你不断调整策略。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不断进化的武器库</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/6ed6e4dc8719dba0ed902dfe80fea21f.poster.avif?t=1771774128\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/6ed6e4dc8719dba0ed902dfe80fea21f.webm?t=1771774128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/6ed6e4dc8719dba0ed902dfe80fea21f.mp4?t=1771774128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不只是塔 - 将塔、防御陷阱和机器人军队组合进你的征服工具库。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结构变体 - 强化版结构的替代形态。双管炮？核弹弹药？</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelite 进程成长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/3e519584e1a45720519a95242047626c.poster.avif?t=1771774128\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/3e519584e1a45720519a95242047626c.webm?t=1771774128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143600/extras/3e519584e1a45720519a95242047626c.mp4?t=1771774128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过庞大的研究树不断推进，解锁升级、内容与新选项，为游戏增加多样性，并迎战更具挑战性的威胁 </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">别忘了加入愿望单并关注游戏，获取最新动态！</h2>",
